dct_title_s: Map of the southern part of Portuguese possessions on the west coast of Africa to illustrate the Earl of Mayo's journey in 1882-1883
dct_description_sm: Route of expedition shown in red. Portions of routes of Leal 1854, Smuts 1864, Green 1865, Hahn 1866, and Anderson 1867 are shown. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes information on flora and fauna. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 5 (1885), no. 8, pp. 458-73; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
